嘟嘟車 (Tuktuk)、Beca、電動三輪車
(Kuliglig)、[Trishaw](http://www.travelwireasia.com/2562/in-pictures-burmas-
many-modes-of-transport/ "http://www.travelwireasia.com/2562/in-pictures-
burmas-many-modes-of-transport/")、Pedicab、Becak、三輪車
(Tricycle)。這些都是在東南亞區域著名且普遍的三輪車。您可以在市中心的街道上看到它們的蹤跡，但政府正試著禁止這些普遍的三輪車和機動人力車行駛於交通要道上。

[![Tuktuk outfitted with anti-bag snatching netting in Phnom Penh, Cambodia.
Photo from Casey Nelson](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2012/02/tuktuk-anti-
snatching.jpg)](http://ltocambodia.blogspot.com/2011/03/be-careful-out-
there.html)

於柬埔寨金邊，嘟嘟車配備有防護網，以免包包被搶。照片由凱賽．奈爾森 (Casey Nelson) 所攝

