Expat](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Cow-in-Tuk-
Tuk-375x281.jpg)](http://www.talesfromanexpat.com/the-ultimate-
onlyincambodia/)

於柬埔寨貢布，嘟嘟車上的牛。照片由外籍人士泰爾斯 (Tales) 所攝

